VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'I\'m especially looking at the rings right now. I think this is a pretty solid frame. To make sure we have all the details we need, I\'m also going to take a screenshot closer up where we can clearly see the face of the subject. That way we have as much details of, you'

[00:39] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'know, the face, the rings, and everything. So, once again, we\'re going to do the same thing, use FX console, take a screenshot, and then we\'re going to jump over to X-Field, go to the image section, and we\'re going to use Nano Banana Pro'

[00:53] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'with the 16 by 9 aspect ratio set to 2K quality, and I always like to select four output. That way I just get more than I really need. And by doing so, you\'re most likely going to have a'

